                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-stone-200">
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-center text-stone-700 mb-2">é¦™èª¿è¶¨å‹¢é›·é”</h3>
                            <div class="chart-container">
                                <canvas id="scentRadarChart"></canvas>
